<item>
<title>“苦瓜”数学家柯西的故事及柯西中值定理</title>
<link>http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/d2Nu8YLVKo</link>
<guid isPermaLink="true" >http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/d2Nu8YLVKo</guid>
<description>&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;span&gt;前方高能转入正题&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.9933333333333334&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;600&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uD4MX8ts0hf5uIGqXsmiaIrG3cc24ngMdRicdJgXVIaYzeqjAmJAWt8s9EPwDY77BTia8v2CPiayX3Jiaw7VvfA8WdA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;拉格朗日中值定理的意思就是：连接图像上两个点 &lt;/span&gt;A, B &lt;span&gt;画一条线，要求画出的线每个点都连续可导，那么你画出的这条线中至少会有一个点处的切线是与连接&lt;/span&gt; A, B &lt;span&gt;的直线平行的。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;我们可以用一个直观的例子说明这个中值定理的意思：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;有一辆汽车加速行驶，用8秒时间将距离从0推进到200米，很容易算出这8秒钟内汽车的平均速度为25米/秒，那么在这8秒内一定有某一时刻汽车的速度正好是25米/秒。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;600&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7233333333333334&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;600&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uD4MX8ts0hf5uIGqXsmiaIrG3cc24ngMdN80DVZRTicP5BTCIVqr0uG8PFIqlTNTKNBicfHpmK2frHO2nz42DKk5w/640?&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;558&quot; data-ratio=&quot;2.235&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;600&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-cropy2=&quot;1341.9354838709676&quot; data-cropy1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropx2=&quot;600&quot; data-cropx1=&quot;0&quot; data-croporisrc=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uD4MX8ts0hf5uIGqXsmiaIrG3cc24ngMdj3xSsXWibAOoss4pGHrD9QntFAdJK5HCg8ibD4xS9vpHNPteXCK2SNGA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLrTWVKNkgnBTHJuqZbAx4xc2pc37EX19FYjUwe9qJAQS19qFKwPBg9A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;柯西中值定理&lt;/span&gt;是拉格朗日中值定理的推广，是微分学的基本定理之一。其几何意义为，用参数方程表示的曲线上至少有一点，它的切线平行于两端点所在的弦。该定理可以视作在参数方程下拉格朗日中值定理的表达形式。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;柯西中值定理粗略地表明，对于两个端点之间的给定平面弧，至少有一个点，弧的切线通过其端点平行于切线。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;与拉氏定理的联系&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;在柯西中值定理中，若取g(x)=x时，则其结论形式和拉格朗日中值定理的结论形式相同。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;因此，拉格朗日中值定理为柯西中值定理的一个特例；反之，柯西中值定理可看作是拉格朗日中值定理的推广。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;/&gt; &lt;strong&gt;证明&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;可构造辅助函数&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;423&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.0425531914893617&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;423&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLicBpkcCiavb6q6GHzx3N5AYUHiaDoHibMoY3agDFtOaPn3HuEqsjDPc2Qw/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; ， &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;32&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5625&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;32&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLfE5tZMbPWc1NYs5HNMibfJnzQKTvexfzaS5auyFe5Dur20LKvltR0icg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 在 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;31&quot; height=&quot;17&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5483870967741935&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;31&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLJO7Jr7hL9La0MagFLichoIYKVuyvicicECxsuzroEWUHdtlOvV3tRa8MQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 上连续，在 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;32&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5625&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;32&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLEE5vVwcmibaly14ruxuBoDMdUszZUHlHTH11voCjzj4RibsR9vbPZOBA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 内可导，且有 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;109&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.1651376146788991&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;109&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLP3aPJ6C7ia79fjHzbeLF1icRnKeJMia6Fzc7WrBym6YUEsIzKasepkzSg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;由罗尔定理可知，存在 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;60&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.3&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;60&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxL3ju9bGaHaNB39qJRCbOYVyp78ianmdAOGyWhGibqYhAVIxqWibOw27e4w/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; ，使得 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;65&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.27692307692307694&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;65&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLFThhIDB2FLDClCsLHUrvQiaibFNbOlR2w7kFVbocRt2iaIiba8olEjNCpg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; ，即 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;294&quot; height=&quot;19&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.06462585034013606&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;294&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLV8DggibXpsIfwaJxYbUmWWEJJ7NQeibk1iceicU1Vic5tjUyAyNntBTyxUQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; ，又 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;61&quot; height=&quot;19&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.3114754098360656&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;61&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLyicZMIz4R96bnXsiaicfQESMl47qs9GfCUAYz5XInDPOibGEwxmzaPKOUA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt;，所以有 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;140&quot; height=&quot;40&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.2857142857142857&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;140&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLlNvjI6PWPsyAMqANUwpCpT1Z4cibqbyLN9xZT458AbbsF05nseB9SOQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;几何意义&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;若令&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;125&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.144&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;125&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLdTicHmb1oibiacH2dAFCXE6yhoazJcy1hfBOial5icsIz7pJ2Gs4GEVnFgg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span&gt;，这个形式可理解为&lt;/span&gt;参数方程&lt;span&gt;，而&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;79&quot; height=&quot;40&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5063291139240507&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;79&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLp2YRnLpz4aiaiab5VIW1TfUNVbuRCshR77llV8V61Puic0ZM57gbXgg4A/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span&gt;则是连接参数曲线两端点弦的斜率，&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;39&quot; height=&quot;40&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.0256410256410255&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;39&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLzrVNw2pXNsRD4IY6nHfpnUBInuCtGzPib5WJmN3KUYPRXqwFN1YqdPw/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span&gt;表示曲线上某点处切线的斜率，在定理的条件下，结论可理解如下：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;220&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.8090909090909091&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;220&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLSZffxVSLEo6830ESeCLz9VVicXbMciccvbLSz7TCZKGe2K613CxP3LoQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;用参数方程表示的曲线上至少有一点，在这一点处的切线平行于连接两个端点的弦。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;/&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;应用例子&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;1）泰勒公式&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;柯西中值定理最主要的应用是证明&lt;span&gt;带有拉格朗日余项的&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;9&quot; height=&quot;8&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.8888888888888888&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;9&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLdJzic8owLmxnOPjLRv8ELetcJCib9Lrvr33ksBbHlXzm5zWjG4MrorHQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span&gt;阶泰勒公式&lt;/span&gt;，只要反复使用柯西中值定理多次就能证明，下面以 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;35&quot; height=&quot;12&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.34285714285714286&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;35&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLgCSmZibe90pa6YBzPtUV7pBcmicEYFicJmryiczibo58BeuPF6MK0Pe9PJA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 为例说明。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;例1&lt;/span&gt;设 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;32&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5625&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;32&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLfQlVbbzJefPsMdfZMTnXLcW1WpqFMuX4LNyOadCq4cSc0TiaIQGl8icQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 在 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;32&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5625&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;32&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLEE5vVwcmibaly14ruxuBoDMdUszZUHlHTH11voCjzj4RibsR9vbPZOBA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 内二次可微，证明：任意的 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;81&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.2222222222222222&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;81&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxL0afafR3b07YoKnnsY9s08eOpJ5dR6LLibhiaLtibdIJXXEvKJQgcjE8Tw/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; ，在 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;30&quot; height=&quot;11&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.36666666666666664&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;30&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxL6P5Mzep0D3YkKMOSJMF5oqY71gEy0J9tThMXwvjRrK3gVhs9VI1Sww/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 之间存在 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;9&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.7777777777777777&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;9&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLKl2l8MWpRiaiaL46j9joKbErTN2tEOm0BtrH4GBgyeuv6azjZsV8F5Ew/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; ，使&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;326&quot; height=&quot;35&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.10736196319018405&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;326&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLrSPHch27MYDF3D823icNIMwvGeiaTpV18ZyuD4EAtxEArjllTVUU8wiaQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;这就是函数 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;32&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5625&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;32&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLfQlVbbzJefPsMdfZMTnXLcW1WpqFMuX4LNyOadCq4cSc0TiaIQGl8icQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 在点 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;15&quot; height=&quot;11&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7333333333333333&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;15&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLY8sMbiaoLGlEYaZwlSeam9zxoaX22cMrcHBF9nSTkyknMvxg7tNggYg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 邻域内的一阶泰勒公式。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;证明&lt;/span&gt;令 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;251&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.07171314741035857&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;251&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLicJW8996y8yCicdgGDKLvYpp1LowlRP1yvIHyBXiczZ4FznlZhKMC0RcA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; ， &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;111&quot; height=&quot;21&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.1891891891891892&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;111&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLu6n5N2DBQ5cakPYUibMhQt8KDzAdZibryYxSsKS7TicicNNVXdibbic16rrA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt;利用 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;127&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.14173228346456693&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;127&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLXQduIFVv3O2XzGibDiamfCSWCJSYwXSpRkhxMXBo6ws0yNMibsxLicQCFg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; ， &lt;/span&gt; &lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;/&gt; &lt;img width=&quot;136&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.1323529411764706&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;136&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLUIzqAHP04ibKE1Gics34h3HzBXethenwcC6HSia2ca4CWKRzxGfJpsyrQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; ， &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;100&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.18&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;100&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLRSiavSzgGwSIld3pQP8ZV8Ztq2u35kf7aUCc4XTmjaCicibeV0c1uWJ3w/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; ， &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;70&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.2571428571428571&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;70&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLfN3TRp9qSPwTAethneiaaG4aMbP8E3PcKQnmxe4WqHqibA7l4obTsx0g/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 。在两次应用到柯西中值定理后可以得到：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;258&quot; height=&quot;44&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.17054263565891473&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;258&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLfsP3Lr4jO3gTP2Ja6qTSt49pZT2k2YpicndwfAAuOWib8Kpc0Eh3ObgQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;438&quot; height=&quot;40&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.091324200913242&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;438&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLsibToH029ianBQkXUJhCl66OIbse3IRriayuoLB0V6IErW5fj5Od7x0FQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;命题得证。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;2）洛必达法则&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;柯西中值定理的一个最重要的应用就是可以推导计算待定型的极限最有效的方法——洛必达法则。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;洛必达法则是求两个无穷小量或两个无穷大量的比的极限。在满足一定条件下可以化成两个函数的导数的比值极限，这样就有可能使得原待定型变成简便而有效的求非待定型极限的问题。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;我们得出下面这个定理（洛必达法则）：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;⑴两个函数 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;32&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5625&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;32&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLfQlVbbzJefPsMdfZMTnXLcW1WpqFMuX4LNyOadCq4cSc0TiaIQGl8icQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 和 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;30&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;30&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLa0CoHmUbe3NEcppua88bqnxCraMNFcYlfqE5iacOS3HLuQR07gqZmWA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 在开区间 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;32&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5625&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;32&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLEE5vVwcmibaly14ruxuBoDMdUszZUHlHTH11voCjzj4RibsR9vbPZOBA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 可微，并且在这个开区间上， &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;30&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;30&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLa0CoHmUbe3NEcppua88bqnxCraMNFcYlfqE5iacOS3HLuQR07gqZmWA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 的导数不等于0；&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;⑵存在极限 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;112&quot; height=&quot;40&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.35714285714285715&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;112&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLRu83c5G43Vmjbe0yJiaqgiaRPBCtMZOvzkkwRjibh0hC5YlR4hG5ytzVg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; （或 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;15&quot; height=&quot;7&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.4666666666666667&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;15&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLhcc8OsRgNKUSwjmeYXKr7o0rGaxeCnebOPC1iaRVx6U5ll1HNdBDkrQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; ），其中A为一个有限的常数。则在以下情况下： &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;193&quot; height=&quot;25&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.12953367875647667&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;193&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLBAqAPHF1ibj2DuRgJzFG0rr2rPSFbSibxSDdTZT4tm5nRtl2iaCMU2rUg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt;（或者 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;108&quot; height=&quot;25&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.23148148148148148&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;108&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLPGhUA5OicSWlaG7O7TjZBiaKdgr4S1g5J4DYGEn8aq3ib0T1Picu3NJd9w/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 和 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;106&quot; height=&quot;25&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.2358490566037736&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;106&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLlGDnatXDrEYw3HgMvzMreW1wo3iafgMXcesQtC2WiaMOawlvgcY4F8sg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; ）。那么就有： &lt;/span&gt; &lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;/&gt; &lt;img width=&quot;210&quot; height=&quot;40&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.19047619047619047&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;210&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxL6FF4MhVrl5FsEw6L20E8sywVlz4VQHrYC5mu6uxQRIw9zUrAia2acSA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; （或 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;15&quot; height=&quot;7&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.4666666666666667&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;15&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLhcc8OsRgNKUSwjmeYXKr7o0rGaxeCnebOPC1iaRVx6U5ll1HNdBDkrQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; ）。在区间的另一个端点也存在相类似的结果。这个定理就称之为洛必达法则，能有效地应用于待定型的极限计算。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;3）不等式&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;柯西中值定理在不等式的证明也有广泛应用，关键是f(x)和g(x)要选得恰当。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;例3&lt;/span&gt;试证明当 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;35&quot; height=&quot;13&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.37142857142857144&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;35&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLXPPmiaCO3fKGMo7zYgr24Y5ibZJ3W5UqgKWJjAL27sicMz6NX01YwlgUA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 时， &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;215&quot; height=&quot;27&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.12558139534883722&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;215&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxL18f4Qre19l8ZEBUR05MtdKDziaQQib0VyahbSIhq7etiaxAJIUiaEAmyww/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;证明 设 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;282&quot; height=&quot;27&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.09574468085106383&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;282&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLMkL5VMibsH8NYs66MLDNddb0CcfyfOhZOxzRbgrZiaEgIC1ye6Q93ayQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; ，则 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;66&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.2727272727272727&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;66&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLcnHAZXmSosCNicgHBYFqDWHdVObpAjGPpw3WibaEMy9fyAU1mtT5aHhw/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 在区间 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;32&quot; height=&quot;17&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.53125&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;32&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLaesbr1dFeb7pYmf1qFicSrpZq4UknZeIGlso4ibIqcdf9hPH4ySzmyVQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 上满足柯西中值定理条件，所以存在 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;61&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.29508196721311475&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;61&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLrhvu6YtLcwKPbFQE6bbaCVejnOibJxfmkic05FREKKNWMW053sibJicj2g/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; ，使 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;141&quot; height=&quot;40&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.28368794326241137&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;141&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLWia58aExicqa3FlZkPawpxwUDbJJUlNTVuxNdfXzTVZ63FGRdkpHBVrg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; ，即&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;244&quot; height=&quot;68&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.2786885245901639&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;244&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLIW2BQcuoQEcFocWENXVrUDiaC6g9SAiaxhJah13zkH4jaJULYmBOW74Q/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;结论得证。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;4）中值点&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;中值点的存在性的证明是柯西中值定理最典型的应用之一。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;例4&lt;/span&gt;设 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;35&quot; height=&quot;13&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.37142857142857144&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;35&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLffUYbArG0MaeHYgicQkNnusI5M9D1EoegOJWym5UlpibxmibyYibHSicxZg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; ，函数 &lt;/span&gt; &lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;/&gt; &lt;img width=&quot;32&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5625&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;32&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLfQlVbbzJefPsMdfZMTnXLcW1WpqFMuX4LNyOadCq4cSc0TiaIQGl8icQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 在区间 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;31&quot; height=&quot;17&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5483870967741935&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;31&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLJO7Jr7hL9La0MagFLichoIYKVuyvicicECxsuzroEWUHdtlOvV3tRa8MQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 上连续，在 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;32&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5625&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;32&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLEE5vVwcmibaly14ruxuBoDMdUszZUHlHTH11voCjzj4RibsR9vbPZOBA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 内可导，则存在 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;60&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.3&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;60&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLxE2OLUSA7HOXVd8PfPicOFicqyRp4HQUYlL7RvFP5ONt60AZO6vsypew/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; ，使得 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;200&quot; height=&quot;59&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.295&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;200&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLmDHjrN4iaibsEfKvFwy5U1YYuicMqkr7cmZOnnqXzEaQvSmaEuKxiaxgibw/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;证明&lt;/span&gt; 设 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;86&quot; height=&quot;35&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.4069767441860465&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;86&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLEG0fH27bcTL5P8REFFVbW4IJWXqg9ibQBUoEgSF2kBY6ibaT2lZeC6mQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; ， &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;63&quot; height=&quot;35&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5555555555555556&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;63&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLs5umlklDLnOiaGu9gaZQpDbialrc3M8kEGevn1vc3PoX7Gkz81rCq2bw/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; ，显然 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;74&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.24324324324324326&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;74&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLAWzYZndjBvheHFZSLyVNrjqxia3uUIpKF9WCxFxEBB8oI1ANazLqKNA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 在 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;31&quot; height=&quot;17&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5483870967741935&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;31&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLJO7Jr7hL9La0MagFLichoIYKVuyvicicECxsuzroEWUHdtlOvV3tRa8MQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; 上满足柯西中值定理的条件，于是存在 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;60&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.3&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;60&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLxE2OLUSA7HOXVd8PfPicOFicqyRp4HQUYlL7RvFP5ONt60AZO6vsypew/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; ，使得&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;352&quot; height=&quot;51&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.14488636363636365&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;352&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLfzCO4VBEpCuiaHEC0CGkprhwIEUHJzSpRchjjRx6lEuyDgc9caBeghw/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;即存在 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;60&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.3&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;60&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLxE2OLUSA7HOXVd8PfPicOFicqyRp4HQUYlL7RvFP5ONt60AZO6vsypew/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; ，使得 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;263&quot; height=&quot;19&quot; title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.07224334600760456&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;263&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/uJcKyGGBIvHPmiaMRx1VEPaeSGIYhEOxLnic0DvjfpPtlQlSKFd2lqESZltLSj4bWpLHzzTJdD79E4GQhPjzGAlA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; ，即可得结论。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
