<description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;起床上班的你&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; class=&quot;__bg_gif&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5619047619047619&quot; data-type=&quot;gif&quot; data-w=&quot;315&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/951TjTgiabkyqTH9cgj8huSubnr9UJvL3brpicoSjh1vr3p9mAIiaFfGjuv3656UjuoBNiarBTWDZica1YuulEe541g/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

